ow\n71\t```\n72\tUser types: leave\n73\tBot: What is your full name?\n74\tUser: Sarah Lim\n75\tBot: ✅ Name: Sarah Lim — What is your role?\n76\tUser: Paramedic\n77\tBot: ✅ Role: Paramedic — What date(s)?\n78\tUser: 10 Jun 2025\n79\tBot: ✅ Date(s): 10 Jun 2025 — What is your Ambulance ID?\n80\tUser: AMB-01\n81\tBot: ✅ Ambulance: AMB-01 — What type of leave?\n82\tUser: MC\n83\tBot: ✅ Leave Type: Medical Leave — Please upload your MC.\n84\tUser: [uploads photo]\n85\tBot: ✅ Document received — Request submitted! Ref: LR-xxx\n86\t```\n87\t"}]},"uuid":"5cb2a2d2-5f58-4799-9983-5a2ab2e27e8a","timestamp":"2026-06-30T10:06:57.068Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"69af39e3-058d-4b5e-ac4d-3955cdd7bde6","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"c:\\Users\\perur\\Downloads\\EFAR_final","sessionId":"4cf68dc3-3ba1-4603-9046-2aaf11e1fce4","version":"2.1.195","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
